OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Fheavy rain will ease through the
OL,7,Fevening, with a few showers possible
OL,8,Fthrough the night, mainly across
OL,9,FCumbria. Some clearer spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping in the south. A mild night
OL,11,Fto come for most places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA dry start, with sunny spells
OL,14,Fin the south and more in the way of
OL,15,Fcloud in the north. Turning wetter
OL,16,Fhere as the day progresses. Warm in
OL,17,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
